{{Infobox website | name = | logo = Civicedu logo.png | logo_size = 200px | logocaption = | screenshot = | collapsible = | collapsetext = | caption = | url = | slogan = | commercial = No | type = [[Online education]] | registration = Required | language = Ukrainian | num_users = | content license = | owner = Global Synergy | author = [[Global Synergy]] | editor = | launch_date = Autumn 2014 (expected) | current_status = In development | footnotes = }} '''Open Civic Education''' ('''CivicEdu''') is a Ukrainian [[massive open online course|massive open online courses (MOOC)]] web-portal with emphasis on civic education. It was initiated by [[Global Synergy]] in March, 2014 and is currently at the development stage. It is expected to open in autumn 2014.<ref>http://nc.gov.ua/news/index.php?ID=1068</ref>
